{"tid":336780,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《正義聯盟》導演薩克薛達唔再做DC電影策劃人？","createTime":"2017-07-26T16:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T01:30:30.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c97b39002c58f0cd4a939c1154aee6369804655e","tid":336780,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:52:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=25384&amp;catid=35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Fmobile%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D25384%26catid%3D35&d=I%2FNeYRLxjsprn22OSVpJsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f9af04bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=25384&amp;catid=35</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》公映後，唔少觀眾質疑導演薩克薛達嘅功力，後來薩克薛達20歲女兒Autumn三月期間自殺離世，令兩夫妻決定抽身離開《正義聯盟》，由Joss Whedon接手後，有消息指薩克薛達將減少參與DCEU嘅整體發展決策。<br />\n現時薩克薛達及其妻子兼拍檔Deborah稱得上係DCEU嘅建築師，而據Mashable「多個消息來源」指，佢哋兩位將減少對DCEU創作上發揮影響力，而Whedon與DC創意總監Geoff Johns會接手建立DC電影宇宙。不過，華納CCO Toby Emmerich發聲明澄清，薛達夫婦仍然係華納大家庭重要組成部分，並正積極參與未來多部DC電影。報導指兩位仍然想花時間同家人一齊，同時決定下一步行動，未來幾部片掛住監製銜頭絕唔出奇，但參與程度未必有之前咁高。"},{"pid":"ea9ace3f2f103205dea6aa8109bb1a5693143fe2","tid":336780,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"唔講dc電影<br />\n佢老婆本身都係華納高層來<br />\n唔拍dc電影<br />\nzs佢都可以隨時開其他戲<br />\n電影就係一門埋班關係網工業<br />\n所以zs真係幾時出返來都大把野撈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ffa2a468b458e8e856767cd1a6d7be0904cbfb","tid":336780,"uid":105605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"DCEU冇Zack好似"},{"pid":"1486d18487e6d3a45dbd8f591d3576eecddc9862","tid":336780,"uid":105605,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:15:16.000Z","msg":"唔該個死肥仔唔好打正聯二既主意，佢啲復聯真係拍到好柒"},{"pid":"573dcb69923be17d8da5f3d7fce3f1488e0afe73","tid":336780,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T22:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該個死肥仔唔好打正聯二既主意，佢啲復聯真係拍到好柒</blockquote><br />\n唔想darkseid打打下係到搞gag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1f26e11ea3477f829b01c50fd57ee2a447ce12","tid":336780,"uid":81397,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:30:30.000Z","msg":"拍flashpoint係Zack idea<br />\n<br />\n所以幫Ben叔Cast 左個勁正既老豆同老母"}]}